{"tid":1623401,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係革命啊大家，大家係咪仲要顧lee樣個樣啊？","createTime":"2019-10-04T20:56:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T21:09:34.000Z","uid":80941,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f656c3f735e1fadc4fc74dbc2524df22140b823e","tid":1623401,"uid":80941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T20:56:58.000Z","msg":"我覺得今晚rb的確有影響到路面情況，<br />\n大家整rb唔可以淨係搬要綁實甚燈柱唔係比啲司機輕易搬走呀屌 ，表示覺得竹魔法師好撚勁<br />\n另外唔明白大家用得火魔法，點解仲會放消防過先，同埋做好rb就真係可以阻礙狗車同消防，次次一放完火啲消防勁快救熄，有撚用咩？<br />\n<br />\n重點係，我地輕輕破壞都係會比政府同藍絲屌，點解要叫大家唔好大大力裝修先？我地要令香港有蒙面法變得更亂，令國際覺得香港政府更無能，緊急法冇撚用。<br />\n<br />\n老實講宜加冇民意可言嫁喇，只要我地贏左，民意先會全數喺我哋尼邊。"},{"pid":"85156ed8cfffec55e40db244829a5cc1315b8255","tid":1623401,"uid":80941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T20:59:25.000Z","msg":"香港人，反抗！"},{"pid":"dcf31205d72da7faa2befa5a07fc926e0aa0b3ae","tid":1623401,"uid":80941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T21:06:37.000Z","msg":"香港人，反抗！"},{"pid":"3000daef61badb019a2da7bdca69c01d9b9a5e70","tid":1623401,"uid":80941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T21:06:47.000Z","msg":"香港人，反抗！"},{"pid":"eb117a19d2da2df48810e956b3665c38d6f0313a","tid":1623401,"uid":80941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T21:06:57.000Z","msg":"香港人，反抗！"},{"pid":"a364c9032ca815d737149a17dc7fc823c63f5567","tid":1623401,"uid":80941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T21:07:07.000Z","msg":"香港人，反抗！"},{"pid":"8b2f343593c65725e41824eb64d0abcbd5cd7783","tid":1623401,"uid":80941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T21:07:19.000Z","msg":"香港人，反抗！"},{"pid":"07cb3e6e8e4973c6c1ae7f46b1685f118f6b8075","tid":1623401,"uid":80941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T21:07:29.000Z","msg":"香港人，反抗！"},{"pid":"a43be018aef6a08a6e002f03484dfb3d13cce961","tid":1623401,"uid":80941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi